        "content": "## 📡 RoleRadar — Phase 1.5 · Archive\n\nFetches full job descriptions, converts them to Markdown, and archives them to Google Drive for later reference.\n\n**In:** `Jobs` tab  •  **Out:** Drive `_archive` + `Archive` tab\n**Optional** — run any time after Phase 1.\n\n— github.com/damran/role-radar\n\n⚙️ **Setup:** open the **Config box** (the first node) and fill in your details, then add your Google + OpenRouter credentials — see docs/CREDENTIALS.md.",
